Qatar Steel to Raise in Saudi Company to 40%, Al Sharq Says

-- B y   R o b e r t   T u t t l e
-- 
2011-11-28T07:24:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-28/qatar-steel-to-raise-in-saudi-company-to-40-al-sharq-says.html
Qatar Steel Co., a unit of
 Industries Qatar (IQCD) , decided to raise its stake in  Saudi Arabia ’s
new South Steel Co. to 40 percent from 30 percent to strengthen
its investments in countries belonging to the Gulf Cooperation
Council,  Al Sharq  reported, siting unidentified people close to
the transaction.  Industries Qatar’s investor relations department didn’t
immediately return an e-mail for comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Robert Tuttle in Doha at 
 rtuttle@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  